  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "1987-02-11", 
    "text": "Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow an income tax credit for expenses incurred for radon-reduction equipment installed in a principal residence. Sets the amount of such credit at 40 percent of such expenditures. Limits to $2,000 the amount of such expenditures which may be taken into account."
